The type is nested 1000 times. Note that this only segfaults for associated constants. Functions are fine:
```rust
// same types as before

trait FnAsNum {
    fn num() -> u32;
}

impl FnAsNum for Z {
    fn num() -> u32 { 0 }
}

impl<T: FnAsNum> FnAsNum for S<T> {
    fn num() -> u32 { T::num() + 1 }
}

fn main() {
    println!("{}", Nested::num());
}
```
This successfully compiles and prints `1000`.
